Subject: [PATCH 9/11] qlcnic: Allow vlan0 traffic
Patch-mainline: Queued in subsystem maintainer repository
Git-repo: git://git.kernel.org/pub/scm/linux/kernel/git/davem/net-next.git
Git-commit: cecd59d84d8e401db7860fc5fae503c965e5c470
References: bnc#853685 FATE#315935

o Adapter allows vlan0 traffic in case of SR-IOV after setting
  QLC_SRIOV_ALLOW_VLAN0 bit even though we do not add vlan0 filters.

